title: 3月24日，据人民日报消息，15岁考上中科大少年班，24岁博士毕业，26岁成为中山大学副教授，如今28岁的陈逸伦正带着多名与自己同龄甚至年长的研究生，围绕“台风”开展研究。陈逸伦坦言：曾因年龄小被质疑，能否带好学生。他说：“我不看学生的第一学历，思维和能力最重要，第一，保证手把手带；第二，不拿学生一作；第三，杂活不让学生干。”有博士生这样评价陈逸伦，“科研上，他很严谨、责任心很强，也很尊重每个人的兴趣爱好。在生活上，陈老师很随和和他怎么‘玩’都行。”
title_en: On March 24, according to the People's Daily, at the age of 15, he was admitted to the Junior Class of Science and Technology of China, graduated with a doctorate at the age of 24, and became an associate professor at Sun Yat-sen University at the age of 26. Now 28-year-old Chen Yilun is leading many graduate students of his own age or even older to carry out research around "typhoons". Chen Yilun said frankly: He was once questioned because of his young age whether he could take students well. He said: "I don't look at students 'primary academic qualifications. Thinking and ability are the most important. First, make sure to be hands-on; second, don't use students as the same; third, don't let students do chores." Some doctoral students commented on Chen Yilun,"In scientific research, he is very rigorous, has a strong sense of responsibility, and respects everyone's interests and hobbies. In life, Teacher Chen is very easy-going and can 'play' with him any way he wants."

title_en: #CUHK students send annual cards to Taiwanese youth video websites #Cross-Strait youth chorus will be better tomorrow. On April 3, Ma Ying-jeou led the Taiwan Youth League to visit Sun Yat-sen University and held exchange gatherings with CUHK leaders and students. At the exchange meeting, the Sun Yat-sen University student folk orchestra played traditional Guangdong music "Beautiful Flowers and Full Moon" and "Bubugao", and Taiwanese students recited and sang "Those Years". Finally, the popular songs of youth cooperation on both sides of the Taiwan Strait were skewered "Grandma's Penghu Bay","The Moon Represents My Heart","Friends" and "Tomorrow Will Be Better", pushing the atmosphere to a climax. (Reporter Jiang Chenglong's video, Shi Xuefan)@ Cross-Strait Talk

title:
颜宁，签约985高校！2024年4月15日，深圳医学科学院与中山大学在中大深圳校区签署战略合作框架协议，双方将围绕生物医学领域的重大科学技术问题开展合作研究，打造教育、科技、人才三位一体的高地，构建生物医药的东方大湾区。深圳医学科学院院长颜宁、深圳医学科学院副院长涂欢、中山大学校长高松、中山大学副校长谢湜等相关领导出席活动并见证签约。深圳医学科学院副院长谭瑛、中山大学常务副校长杨清华代表合作双方签署协议。 
根据协议，双方将探索科教融汇新机制，本着“研学共建、优势互补、资源共享、合作共赢”的原则，在科学研究、人员双聘、学生培养、资源共享、成果转化及推进高水平国际交流合作等方面深化合作，共同推动粤港澳大湾区生物医药的高质量发展。
title_en:
Yan Ning, signed a contract with 985 universities! On April 15, 2024, Shenzhen Academy of Medical Sciences and Sun Yat-sen University signed a strategic cooperation framework agreement at the Shenzhen Campus of CUHK. The two parties will carry out cooperative research around major scientific and technological issues in the field of biomedicine to create a highland where education, science and technology, and talents are in one. Build the Eastern Greater Bay Area of biomedicine. Yan Ning, President of Shenzhen Academy of Medical Sciences, Tu Huan, Vice President of Shenzhen Academy of Medical Sciences, Gao Song, President of Sun Yat-sen University, Xie Shi, Vice President of Sun Yat-sen University and other relevant leaders attended the event and witnessed the signing of the contract. Tan Ying, Vice President of Shenzhen Academy of Medical Sciences, and Yang Qinghua, Executive Vice President of Sun Yat-sen University, signed the agreement on behalf of both parties. 
According to the agreement, the two sides will explore a new mechanism for the integration of science and education, and follow the principles of "joint construction of research and learning, complementary advantages, resource sharing, and win-win cooperation", deepen cooperation in scientific research, dual recruitment of personnel, student training, resource sharing, achievement transformation and Promote high-level international exchanges and cooperation to jointly promote the high-quality development of biomedicine in the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macao Greater Bay Area.

title_en: "He recorded fairy tales for me every day and flew to South Korea to visit me. In the end, I agreed to propose." In 2005, the Ministry of Education issued new regulations that no longer restrict college students from getting married. Zeng Peilun, a female student at Sun Yat-sen University in 2012, attracted the attention of major media and heated discussions due to her experience of getting married and having children during her undergraduate course, making her famous for a time. In June 2017, National People's Congress students took their children to take graduation photos and became popular, and netizens praised the winners in life. Ten years have passed, Zeng Peiren has become the financial support of the family, and her husband has become a full-time husband. Now, what does she think of her original choice?# College students #What is the meaning of marriage #How couples get along #Exploring hundreds of temperatures for a good life

title: 河南大学创立于1912年，始名河南留学欧美预备学校，首任校长为林伯襄先生，校园选建于河南贡院 旧址之上。后历经中州大学 、 国立开封中山大学 （ 又称国立第五中山大学 ）、省立河南大学 等阶段 ，1942年升格为国立河南大学 。 1952年院系调整 ，部分院系或独立建校或并入兄弟高校，校本部更名为河南师范学院 。后又经开封师范学院 、河南师范大学 等阶段，1984年恢复河南大学 校名。 2008年10月，学校进入省部共建高校行列。2017年9月，学校入选首批国家“双一流”建设高校。2022年2月，学校再次入选国家“双一流”建设高校。111年来，学校恪守“明德新民，止于至善”的校训，形成“团结、勤奋、严谨、朴实”的校风和以“百折不挠、自强不息”为核心的大学精神，培养70多万名各类人才，为教育振兴、科技创新、文化传承、社会进步和人类文明作出突出贡献。#河南大学明伦校区 #百年名校河南大学
title_en: Henan University was founded in 1912. It was originally named Henan Preparatory School for Studying in Europe and America. The first president was Mr. Lin Boxiang. The campus was built on the former site of Henan Gongyuan. Later, it went through stages such as Zhongzhou University, National Sun Yat-sen University in Kaifeng (also known as the Fifth National Sun Yat-sen University), and Provincial Henan University. In 1942, it was upgraded to National Henan University. In 1952, the departments were adjusted, and some departments were established independently or merged into sister universities. The school headquarters was renamed Henan Normal University. Later, through Kaifeng Normal University and Henan Normal University, the name of Henan University was restored in 1984. In October 2008, the school entered the ranks of universities jointly constructed by provinces and ministries. In September 2017, the school was selected as one of the first batch of national "double first-class" construction universities. In February 2022, the school was once again selected as a national "double first-class" construction university. Over the past 111 years, the school has adhered to the school motto of "Be virtuous and new people, and be committed to perfection", formed a school spirit of "unity, diligence, rigor and simplicity" and a university spirit with "perseverance and self-improvement" as the core, and cultivated more than 700,000 talents of various types, making outstanding contributions to educational revitalization, scientific and technological innovation, cultural inheritance, social progress and human civilization.# Henan University Minglun Campus #Centenary Famous University Henan University
